  <para>
   <informaltable>
    <tgroup cols="2">
     <thead>
      <row>
       <entry>&Version;</entry>
       <entry>&Description;</entry>
      </row>
     </thead>
     <tbody>
      <row>
       <entry>5.5.8</entry>
       <entry>
        Trying to implement <classname>DateTimeInterface</classname> raises a
        fatal error now. Formerly implementing the interface didn't raise an
